# ARXML round-trip fixtures (5 user BSW samples from S32K148_EAS_EB_3399A).
# Sprint 0-1 kept them gitignored because parser/serializer unit tests hit
# the 80% coverage gate on their own. Sprint 2 adds 5-sample mutation
# round-trip (T7) which depends on these, so they are now in-repo.

# Local reference ARXML (not shipped templates).
# `samples/arxml/<id>/` is the convention for shipped templates (see samples/README.md).
# Flat `AUTOSAR_MOD_*.arxml` here is the full AUTOSAR R21-11 standard ECUC parameter
# definition (~15 MB) — kept as a local reference fixture, not shipped via electron-builder.
samples/arxml/AUTOSAR_MOD_*.arxml

