# Local regeneration scripts (one-off per project, not part of repo)
# e.g. claude-AutosarCfg/regenerate.ts is a personal script with hard-coded
# absolute paths to user ECUC fixtures, not a repo-shipped tool.
claude-AutosarCfg/

# Local Claude Code scratch space (spec-driven dev session reports + reviews).
# Kept on disk for the active session; never committed.
.claude/